{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1775528964.287954", "card_id": "Q_2022303887835619414", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 189}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "研究称午睡时间超过 1 小时死亡风险增加 30%，这是真的吗？午睡怎么睡、睡多久才是最科学的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[视频]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-213c1ecc27cacf1c1dc48961fef47d2d_720w.webp"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "497 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2022303887835619414"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIgd+/xqeT5v5JEAMaCTExODk2OTA5MSCjtq3OBjAAOMcDQAByEzIwMjIzMDM4ODc4MzU2MTk0MTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1775528964.289130", "card_id": "Q_2024406743845794724", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 72}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "男子用 AI 写歌仅版权就赚了五位数，AI 还能怎样用来变现？各地「一人公司」扶持政策能带来哪些利好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "「一个人加上 AI 就是一间公司」，正在逐步变为现实。 近期，AI「一人公司」（OPC, One Person Company）创业话题引发关注。根据 Carta 2025 年的数据，独立创始人创立公司的比例从 2019 年的 23.7% 跃升至 2025 年上半年的 36.3%，六年间增长了 53%。在国内，2025 年上半年一人公司新注册数同比增长 47%。 日前，红星资本局采访了多位「AI+ 一人公司」创业者。他们中，有人从老板身份回归「全能员工」，利润率比以往提升了 20% 至 30%；有人创建的网站开始密集上线新功能，日活超 20 万，已有创投机构向其发出邀请，目前公司估值已超 3000 万元。还有人一边把「主业」做得风生水起，一边为财务、法律等等问题头疼，选择入驻 OPC 孵化园区，政策宣讲、投资对接、创业培训等支持成了创业的及时雨。 对于 AI 时代的「一人公司」，工信部信息通信经济专家委员会委员盘和林认为，当技术工具变成人人可得的基础设施时，OPC 只是 AI 应用类企业的一种组织模式，所以要实质大于形式地发展 OPC，同时需有效降低交易成本、优化营商环境，并配套大量的人才激励政策。 …「一人公司」创业者「用 AI 雇人类」，公司估值已超 3000 万！还有老板用 AI 当「员工」：没了管理成本和人员开支，利润率提升了 20% 至 30%"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-84507ed80cf4ecbd13aa8aac0cae24d2_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "165 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2024406743845794724"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIgd+/xqeT5v5JEAMaCTExOTAzNzg0MSCTg8zOBjAAOMQCQAFyEzIwMjQ0MDY3NDM4NDU3OTQ3MjR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1775528964.290468", "card_id": "Q_1976920485582369579", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 95}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《西游记》是不是漏写了一块，在取经路上，是谁给师徒四人理发？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "唐僧估计月月得理发，因为还没成佛。猪八戒，孙悟空，沙僧在凡间吃五谷，毛发肯定会生长，理发师是不可或缺的角色，作者怎么遗漏了呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-8261201b33aef8b5908006abd75a7a18_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "120 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1976920485582369579"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIgd+/xqeT5v5JEAMaCTExNzQ3NTE4OCCNgZnJBjAAOHtAAnITMTk3NjkyMDQ4NTU4MjM2OTU3OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1775528964.292162", "card_id": "Q_2024250301692027403", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2026 年清明档总票房 3.04 亿，相较去年继续下降，如何评价这个成绩？对行业会产生什么影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如题："}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d9b04b74ce386f5cea6105300667cdfb_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "116 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2024250301692027403"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIgd+/xqeT5v5JEAMaCTExOTAzNTMyMCDg38nOBjAAOCpAA3ITMjAyNDI1MDMwMTY5MjAyNzQwM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1775528964.293345", "card_id": "Q_2024233073366099524", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 167}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "黄晓明就带 9 岁儿子骑行发文道歉，称已去交警部门接受处罚，未成年儿童骑车有哪些容易被忽视的安全问题？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "4 月 5 日，演员黄晓明发文： 大家好，我是黄晓明。今天我必须为自己的疏忽郑重道歉。昨日正值假期，我和小朋友也趁着春光户外骑行，本意是享受大自然，却在网友地提示下才知道，自己忽略了《中华人民共和国道路交通安全法实施条例》中「驾驶自行车须年满 12 周岁」的规定，对此我深感愧疚。作为父亲，我本该以身作则，时刻把孩子的安全与遵守法规放在首位。借此机会，也想和所有家长朋友们共勉：孩子学会骑车不等于可以上路，交通安全容不得半分疏忽，遵守法规才是对孩子最好的保护。再次为我的错误向大家致歉，未来我一定会更加严谨。刚刚我已经去交警部门接受处罚，但还在假期，工作人员建议节后过来，所以我会在上班时间再到相关交警部门接受处罚和批评教育，再次感谢大家的监督和提醒。 此前报道： 4 月 4 日，黄晓明通过微博发布照片，照片中，他本人骑着共享单车，9 岁的儿子则骑着普通儿童自行车，在人行道前击掌、合影。 黄晓明就带 9 岁儿子骑行发文道歉：已经去交警部门接受处罚"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-9edebf63bba6ecf66fa0836fa708a740_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "115 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2024233073366099524"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIgd+/xqeT5v5JEAMaCTExOTAzNDY4NiDVv8nOBjAAOM8CQARyEzIwMjQyMzMwNzMzNjYwOTk1MjR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1775528964.294954", "card_id": "Q_2024602630173848195", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 210}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美以袭击伊朗进入第 39 天，当前局势如何？哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "○特朗普称 7 日 20 时是伊朗「最后期限」 ○伊朗已回应美方停战提议并提出十项要求 ○伊朗打击美「的黎波里」号两栖攻击舰 ○美公布营救飞行员行动细节国际新闻早知道丨特朗普威胁伊朗 7 日 20 时是「最后期限」 伊朗就美停战提议提出十项要求"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-2b9465d251a507785fc4809b28caacfb_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "115 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2024602630173848195"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIgd+/xqeT5v5JEAMaCTExOTA0NTY5MyCC8M7OBjAAOIIEQAVyEzIwMjQ2MDI2MzAxNzM4NDgxOTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1775528964.295882", "card_id": "Q_2023420406791422348", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 33}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "广州明确传统早茶食品必须 24 小时现制，新规 5 月施行，对此你怎么看？现制是早茶的灵魂吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "守护「一盅两件」烟火气，广州为「早茶传承保护」立法！《广州早茶传承保护规定》将于 2026 年 5 月 1 日起施行。立法明确，传统早茶食品 24 小时现制，收取茶位费要提供配套服务，这保护的不只是手工技艺，更是完整的饮食方式。而立法的另一条主线，是对「人」的关注：尊重消费者的知情权与选择权，保障经营者的公平竞争环境，也让坚守传统的手艺人被看见、被尊重。 详见： 广州早茶新规 5 月 1 日正式施行！ - 21 财经"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-4cdcf34e889456a5f2bec65ee33b5541_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "115 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2023420406791422348"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIgd+/xqeT5v5JEAMaCTExOTAwOTgzNSD61b3OBjAAOD5ABnITMjAyMzQyMDQwNjc5MTQyMjM0OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1775528964.296774", "card_id": "Q_2023921571987759971", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价皇马 1:2 马略卡，基本宣告本赛季四大皆空？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-696db7f285ce09a884dd2789c43ac30e_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "111 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2023921571987759971"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIgd+/xqeT5v5JEAMaCTExOTAyNjEzNSC5+8TOBjAAOB9AB3ITMjAyMzkyMTU3MTk4Nzc1OTk3MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1775528964.297176", "card_id": "Q_20156217", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-